text: This study was conducted from January 2016 to August 2016. A total of 4069 participants were assessed for eligibility, and 3664 participants were enrolled and randomized ( Figure 1 ). Of these participants, three withdrew the consent before the vaccination, and 3661 participants received the vaccination.
